Subject: [PATCH 1075/1594] MLK-10782-4 ARM:imx6qdl:dts:Add LDB_DI_CLK parent
 to device tree.

commit 78cc52b7c90f2d69e7a62f7d36b93221279101bf from
git://git.freescale.com/imx/linux-2.6-imx.git

Add the LDB clock parents to the device tree.

Signed-off-by: Fabio Estevam <fabio.estevam@freescale.com>
Signed-off-by: Ranjani Vaidyanathan <Ranjani.Vaidyanathan@freescale.com>
---
 arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6qdl-sabreauto.dtsi |    2 ++
 arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6qdl-sabresd.dtsi   |    5 +++++
 2 files changed, 7 insertions(+), 0 deletions(-)

diff --git a/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6qdl-sabreauto.dtsi b/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6qdl-sabreauto.dtsi
index e6b686c..91a1e21 100644
